name: Louis V. JACKVONY, Jr. et al. v. Anthony MONAFO et al.

opinions.text:
ORDER
Treating the Town’s appeal as a properly filed petition for writ of certiorari, said petition is hereby denied.
BEVILACQUA, C. J., did not participate.

Donald J. Nasif, Town Sol., Warren, for defendants-petitioners.
